WEBVTT

00:01.151 --> 00:02.317
[Ralph Angel] <i> Previously</i>
<i> on</i>  Queen Sugar...

00:02.353 --> 00:03.593
[woman]
You're now officially
on the roster

00:03.595 --> 00:05.087
as permanent foster parents
in the state of Louisiana.

00:05.089 --> 00:07.965
You're standing for us,
for your father.

00:07.967 --> 00:10.926
My pop
just wanted me to excel,
be some kind of A student.

00:10.928 --> 00:12.886
-You felt like
you disappointed him.
-Definitely.

00:12.888 --> 00:14.805
Would you move
to Africa with me?

00:14.807 --> 00:16.932
[Nova] <i> Dominic,</i>
<i> this is your destiny,</i>
<i> not mine.</i>

00:16.934 --> 00:18.559
Mom, I got a job offer.

00:18.635 --> 00:20.144
-Plan is
to drop out of Xavier.
-[Charley] <i> What?</i>

00:20.146 --> 00:21.595
I'm not asking
for your permission.

00:21.597 --> 00:23.480
-I think we should tell him.
-[Darla] He already knows

00:23.482 --> 00:25.816
<i> you're not</i>
<i> his biological father. No.</i>

00:25.818 --> 00:27.443
You know
they're gonna auction off
his land?

00:27.445 --> 00:29.028
[Ralph] Our land's
right in the middle of it.

00:29.780 --> 00:30.738
[By Your Side
by Sade Adu plays]

00:42.084 --> 00:44.835
-Yeah!
-[all cheering]

00:49.717 --> 00:53.135
The man of the hour.
Our very own superstar.

00:53.220 --> 00:56.180
Saint Jo's
newest, blackest,
beautifulest

00:56.223 --> 00:58.182
school board member,
Mr. Hollywood.

00:58.184 --> 01:00.100
Drinks on him!

01:05.399 --> 01:06.456
Woo!

01:06.458 --> 01:08.192
[By Your Side
continues playing]

02:00.412 --> 02:01.411
Outside?

02:03.624 --> 02:05.040
Under the moonlight.

02:07.002 --> 02:09.002
[laughs slyly]

02:21.600 --> 02:22.516
Hi.

02:24.520 --> 02:25.853
Feel like coming over?

02:36.907 --> 02:39.741
[NOVA
by Me'Shell Ndegéocello plays]

02:39.776 --> 02:41.368
<i> ♪ Dreams never die ♪</i>

02:41.370 --> 02:43.829
<i> ♪ Take flight</i>
<i> as the world turns ♪</i>

02:43.864 --> 02:45.164
<i> ♪ Dreams never die ♪</i>

02:45.240 --> 02:47.749
<i> ♪ Take flight</i>
<i> as the world turns ♪</i>

02:47.751 --> 02:49.293
<i> ♪ Keep the colors</i>
<i> in the lines ♪</i>

